{
  "stem": "2539.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was determined that I'm going to fight to the last drop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was going to boil up some water and pour it over them when they entered the-- the kitchen or the room to get us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was convinced that I'm going to fight to the last drop of my blood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And anyway, and later on-- well, OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father came home and said, tomorrow they need some women and children to-- for a harvest in-- in-- in a village.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I want you and Lola to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Lola went in the morning to get the permission from the [NON-ENGLISH] to-- to leave, and she didn't come in time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father gave a signal, and the column took away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, and the children, and mothers-- we found-- found ourself in a-- in a small place somewhere-- I don't know-- 30 kilometers away from Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We walked, of course, by foot, naturally, and slept in a stable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the following day, the Ukrainian guy told me that they're killing the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a big holiday in Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're killing the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I spread the news.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I-- after I-- he told me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we got to the stable, there was no one there already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In any case, I-- in that field, there was a fellow there who came to collect the straw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were several, but one came up to me and said, are you Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Goldstein's daughter?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, well, I used to deliver timber to your family every winter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had fireplaces, you see, in-- not open-- closed fireplaces-- in every room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the climate there is very harsh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he used to deliver timber, because there was wood-- wood fireplaces there were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, yes, I'm Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
